longBusinessSummary: Freeze Tag, Inc. develops and publishes mobile social games for consumers and businesses worldwide. The company markets, sells, and distributes its games through direct-to-consumer digital storefronts, such as Apple's App Store, the Google Play Store, and Amazon's App Store; and sells players directly through its Websites, such as freezetag.com and store.freezetag.com. It also publishes titles on other platforms, such as the Facebook App Store and Mac App Store, as well as on PC download portals, such as Big Fish Games and others. The company was founded in 2005 and is headquartered in Tustin, California.
